(1292, '2021/12/22', '9:12 a.m.', 'N/A', '10', 'Jimmy Fitzgerald', 'English', 'Writing - Paragraph & Composition Construction', 'The Writing Process - Plan, Compose, Revise, Edit, Publish (by reading, speaking, media presentation)', 'Articulate/Explain the stages of the writing process', 'Juno Galang', 'Achieved', 'N/A', 'Attended Ontime', 'Yes', 'Completed', 'N/A', 'N/A', NULL, '<p><strong>T4 WK10</strong></p><ul><li><strong>The Writing Process</strong><br>Plan<br>Compose<br>Revise<br>Edit&nbsp;<br>Publish</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Quality Literature</strong><br><i><strong>Reading</strong></i></p><ul><li>The Little Prince &nbsp;- Saint-Exupery<br>Analysis</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Creative Writing</strong></p><ul><li>Paragraph<br>Monster Hunter</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><i>Jimmy has really impressed with the amount of writing and creativity he is willing to try and achieve each lesson. At this point, he has become quite used to the creative writing structure we use for our character creation exercises (Name/Appearance/Skills/Diet/Personality) so next te', NULL, '2021-12-22 09:12:58', '2021-12-22 09:39:18'),
