(1295, '2022/01/11', '9:44 a.m.', 'Summer', '1', 'Owen Mclaren', 'English', 'Reading - Comprehension > Text Type & Mental Actions', 'Mental Actions of Reading', 'Monitor comprehension of words, phrases & sentences', 'Juno Galang', 'Achieved', 'N/A', 'Attended Ontime', 'N/A', 'Completed', 'N/A', 'N/A', NULL, '<p>Assessments:</p><ul><li>Morrison McCall</li><li>Burt Word</li><li>Waddington Reading - Had some trouble reading</li><li>PAST - Relatively confident</li><li>Written Phonogram</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Writing:</p><ul><li>About me - Interests</li></ul><p><i>Owen was open and friendly, but displayed a lot of hesitation and nervousness with spelling and reading! He was able to do the spelling and reading tests (completed half) after some encouragement.</i></p>', NULL, '2022-01-11 09:45:02', '2022-01-11 13:54:55'),
