(1370, '2022/02/10', '4:55 p.m.', '1', '1', 'Callisto Pratten', 'Mathematics', 'Money & Financial Maths', 'Solve problems involving simple interest', 'TEXT BOOK - EXERCISES, QUESTIONS, ACTIVITIES', 'Rosemary Beswick', 'Achieved', 'Achieved', 'Attended Ontime', 'N/A', 'Completed', 'N/A', 'N/A', '<p>I collected some materials from Callisto\'s teacher so that she could make a start on her Maths work for the year. We started with a bit of a discussion on the overall structure of the course and the use of the graphics calculator. We then moved onto a review of simple interest calculations. Callisto did these well and set out her work carefully. We worked on questions that just required plugging numbers into the formula and then moved on to some examples where the formula needed to be rearranged.</p>', '<p>I collected some materials from Callisto\'s teacher so that she could make a start on her Maths work for the year. We started with a bit of a discussion on the overall structure of the course and the use of the graphics calculator. We then moved onto a review of simple interest calculations. Callisto did these well and set out her work carefully. We worked on questions that just required plugging numbers into the formula and then moved on to some examples where the formula needed to be rearranged.</p>', NULL, '2022-02-10 16:55:27', '2022-02-10 17:50:08'),
