(1425, '2022/02/18', '7:46 a.m.', '1', '2', 'Gus Pettit', 'Mathematics', 'Number & Place Value', 'Apply the associative, commutative and distributive laws to aid mental and written computation', 'TEXT BOOK - EXERCISES, QUESTIONS, ACTIVITIES', 'Ivan Botero', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Attended Ontime', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', '<p>Today Gus and I were working on algebra; Gus forgot some key operations but with a quick refresh he was able to do the problems which I brought for today’s lesson.&nbsp;</p><p>I told him about Carl F. Gaus, this is a scene from his movie, “Measuring the world”. It’s in German but I reckon the maths part speak by itself. <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n2E_lfc2Bvc\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n2E_lfc2Bvc</a> If you could show this short video to Gus, it would be amazing.&nbsp;</p><p>I gave him some homework to do, in case Gus needs help with it, please don’t hesitate to let me know it.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '2022-02-18 07:46:34', '2022-03-06 18:49:12'),
