(1512, '2022/02/24', '4:28 p.m.', '1', '2', 'Finlay Tueno', 'Mathematics', 'Ratios', 'Unit Ratios & Scale Factors', 'Text book - Exercises, Questions, Activities', 'Ivan Botero', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Attended Ontime', 'N/A', 'Completed', 'N/A', 'N/A', '<p>Work done:</p><ul><li>Rates.</li><li>Ratios.</li><li>Scales.</li><li>Solving short word problems.</li></ul><p>Fin did a great job, we focused on applying those concepts to solve problems related to plumbing. &nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, '2022-02-24 16:28:05', '2022-03-26 10:37:59'),
(1513, '2022/02/24', '4:32 p.m.', '1', '3', 'Finn Mackey', 'English', 'Writing - Sentence Construction & Vocabulary', 'Elements of a compound sentence > Capital letter, two independent clauses joined by a coordinating conjunction (FANBOYS), ending punctuation', 'Articulate/Explain the elements of a compound sentence (include use of manipulatives)', 'Laree Thorsby', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Attended Ontime', 'Yes', 'Completed', 'Assigned', 'N/A', NULL, '<p>T1W3</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>OPR a e I o u y ow ou ough ea ew ui&nbsp; ti si ci sh&nbsp;dge tch</p><p>WPR – ow ou&nbsp; oo a e I o u y sh ti si ci&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>SD – though through rough cough thought drought&nbsp;</p><p>Parts of Speech</p><p>Verbs</p><p>Nouns/pronouns</p><p>Adjectives</p><p>Adverbs</p><p>Worksheets identify POS in sentences.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The Writing Process</p><ol><li>Sentence Structure - Simple sentences elements review + intro to compound. Use HW sentences to make compound sentences.&nbsp;</li><li>Sentence Types - Fact/command/question/emotion</li></ol><p>Sentence structure simple 1 idea independent clause. (Blocks ) and Compound</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>Ho', NULL, '2022-02-24 16:32:27', '2022-03-06 21:06:54'),
