(1523, '2022/02/25', '3:41 p.m.', '1', '3', 'Connor Thompson', 'English', 'Writing - Paragraph & Composition Construction', 'Essay Structure', 'See Notes', 'Neve Mitchell', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Attended Ontime', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', NULL, '<figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>Connor had brought in his history essay for assistance.&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>Highlighted key words in the question. Highlighted key words in the rubric and explained meaning where necessary.&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>Had Connor dot point what information had to go in his essay. I essentially handed it to him and did the mental actions work of decoding the question/necessary information to go in his essay.</td></tr><tr><td>Chunked out the 300-500 words into each part of the question. Brainstormed existing knowledge in dot points. Connor had little existing knowledge from school. He struggled to form his own inferences from what I suggested (e.g. “How', NULL, '2022-02-25 15:41:13', '2022-03-03 15:04:25'),
