(1558, '2022/03/02', '9:27 a.m.', '1', '4', 'Brock Smith', 'English', 'Systematic Phonics - High Frequency Vocabulary', 'Analysis of word structure and application of learned concepts (sounds, phonograms, rules)', 'Spelling Dictation - Precisely say, write and read words in Section L', 'Yina Peng', 'Achieved', 'Achieved', 'Attended Ontime', 'Yes', 'Completed', 'Assigned', 'N/A', NULL, '<ol><li>Kilpatrick F2</li><li>OPR/WPR: o, ui,ew,ck,sh,</li><li>Syllable sorting game(open/closed syllable)</li><li>SD: able-dash</li><li>reviewed rule 25, 13, and rule 4.&nbsp;</li><li>Sentence structure: reviewed simple sentence, briefly introduced compound sentence and send homework related to this.&nbsp;</li></ol><p>Brock does not like reading and spelling, which I would thing of integrating these within games.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2022-03-02 09:28:21', '2022-03-22 09:16:21'),
(1559, '2022/03/02', '1:48 p.m.', '1', '4', 'Angel King', 'English', 'Systematic Phonics - Sounds/Symbols (phonograms)', 'Precisely say and write common phonograms', 'Oral Phonogram Review (OPR) with Stated Purpose - Various Phonograms (see notes)', 'Laree Thorsby', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Attended Ontime', 'Yes', 'Completed', 'Assigned', 'N/A', NULL, '<p>PA – DK d 1: syllable. NW</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>OPR</p><p>A e I o u y wr&nbsp; wh ea oo ai ay oi oy</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>WPR ea &nbsp;wh wr&nbsp; u o I e a y oo ay ai oi oy&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Rule review Rule 4 – game&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>SD:&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Music duty again&nbsp;away begin reset clover over</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Sentence dictation:</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Begin to jump over the log.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>(Nouns/verbs/adjectives)</p><p>Shade words in sentence</p><p>Give Physical examples of Verbs – List onto green paper&nbsp;</p><p>Search for N/V/A in OF passage. (after reading) Panda)</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Game</strong>: Spin a star/Roll th', NULL, '2022-03-02 13:48:15', '2022-03-06 20:42:38'),
