(1612, '2022/03/06', '6:31 p.m.', '1', '1', 'Gus Pettit', 'Mathematics', 'Number & Place Value', 'BODMAS', 'TEXT BOOK - EXERCISES, QUESTIONS, ACTIVITIES', 'Ivan Botero', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Attended Ontime', 'N/A', 'Completed', 'Assigned', 'N/A', NULL, '<p>In our first lesson of the year, Gus and I were working on BODMAS with integers.</p><p>In the beginning, Gus was a little bit lost in terms of not knowing which operation he has to do first. After we did about 10 problems on the board, he was less confused and more confident on how to solve problems with order of operations. &nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2022-03-06 18:37:18', '2022-03-06 18:45:49'),
