(1820, '2022/03/22', '11:12 a.m.', '1', '7', 'Henry Badcock', 'Mathematics', 'Number & Place Value', 'Investigate and use the properties of odd and even numbers', 'TEXT BOOK - EXERCISES, QUESTIONS, ACTIVITIES', 'Laree Thorsby', NULL, NULL, 'Attended Ontime', 'Not Returned', 'Completed', 'N/A', 'N/A', NULL, '<p>Patterns and sequencing</p><p>Focus: Friends of 10/18</p><p>On whiteboard - recognise the patterns</p><p>Complete workbook activity by writing Friends of 18 as addition problems</p><p>Focus - Odd/even numbers</p><p>Identify each (worksheet)</p><p>Define each - odd numbers cannot be divided equally in half/two/two groups/sets. Even numbers can be divided in half/by 2 etc</p><p>PV Dice game - roll 3 dice, add together, write number in chart, odd or even, greater or less than??&nbsp;</p><p>Focus: Patterns</p><p>Identify the missing numbers in a sequence.&nbsp;</p><p>Simple addition/subtraction of numbers less than 10, include across 9-10.&nbsp;</p><p>eg 31 35 39 43 47 51 55 59 63 67 71 75 79', NULL, '2022-03-22 11:13:16', '2022-03-22 11:34:20'),
(1821, '2022/03/22', '11:52 a.m.', '1', '6', 'Angel King', 'English', 'Systematic Phonics - Language Rules (Pronunciation/Spelling/Grammar)', 'Rule 5: i and y may say their second (long) sound at the end of a syllable', 'See Notes', 'Laree Thorsby', NULL, NULL, 'Attended Ontime', 'Yes', 'Completed', 'Assigned', 'N/A', NULL, '<p>T1W5/6</p><p>PA – DK d 3: syllable.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>OPR</p><p>A e I o u y wr&nbsp; wh ea oo ai ay oi oy au aw ew ui ow ou er ir ur wor ear or ar&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>WPR&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><ol><li>Rule review Rule 4 sort &nbsp;</li><li>Rule review Rule 5 sort</li><li>Rule review 6</li></ol><p>&nbsp;</p><p>SD:&nbsp;</p><ol><li>Even crazy emu duo</li><li>Silent my cry quiet</li></ol><p>Mark for rules 4/5/6</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Sentence dictation:</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I am very quiet when I cry.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;((Nouns/verbs/adjectives)</p><p>Shade words in sentence</p><p>Give Physical examples of Verbs – List onto green paper&nbsp;</p><p>Search fo', NULL, '2022-03-22 11:52:58', '2022-03-22 11:55:04'),
