(1884, '2022/03/28', '4:31 p.m.', '1', '9', 'Zac Pharaoh', 'Mathematics', 'OTHER', 'OTHER', 'Please read comments', 'Ivan Botero', 'In Progress', 'N/A', 'Attended Ontime', 'N/A', 'Completed', 'N/A', 'N/A', NULL, '<p>Zac\'s test was about creating a budget to apply the concepts of mean, mode, range and median. Increase and decrease by percentage, and best buys to cover word problems.&nbsp;</p><p>The test didn\'t go as good as I was expecting, we need to work on these concepts later during the year.&nbsp;</p><p>Zac did a good job applying the knowledge to solve the part related to data. However, the rest was a bit difficult for him to process.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Lesson No 9 was delivered on 11.04.2022</p>', '2022-03-28 16:31:26', '2022-07-03 21:08:24'),
