(1899, '2022/03/29', '5:50 p.m.', '1', '8', 'Tyler Van Nimwegen', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Juno Galang', NULL, NULL, 'Attended Ontime', 'Yes', 'Completed', 'Assigned', 'N/A', NULL, '<p>This week, Tyler and I did a coaching session over Zoom, and we were able to finish his Health assignment! Tyler was tasked to reformat his remaining notes from last week, conduct research on specific topics, such as rehabilitation centres only in Tasmania, and to revisit the topic of inpatient vs. outpatient. He also undertook the writing process regarding publishing, and we formatted his fonts, spacing, and bullet points according to academic guidelines issued by his teacher. Tyler was much more open to being guided today, whilst retaining his opinionated nature and made some excellent contributions regarding how he thinks a sentence should be structured and which words sounded best to ', NULL, '2022-03-29 17:50:35', '2022-03-29 17:53:24'),
