(1901, '2022/03/30', '9:55 a.m.', '1', '8', 'Nina Gust', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Juno Galang', NULL, NULL, 'Attended Ontime', 'N/A', 'Completed', 'N/A', 'N/A', NULL, '<p>Phonemic Awareness<br>Kilpatrick: H2 Notes<br>• (Speed) This task was completed quickly<br>• The student found some difficulty with only one word, trick to brick (bick)<br>• However, the student showed confidence with the rest of the task!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>OPR<br>31-38<br>• (Speed) This task was completed at a regular pace<br>• The student found some difficulty with remembering the four sounds of /ou/</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>WPR<br>31-38<br>• (Speed) This task was completed quickly<br>• The student found some difficulty with recalling /ay/ as a phonogram that can be used<br>• However, the student showed confidence with the rest of the task<br>• They were able to complete the entire set<br>• ', NULL, '2022-03-30 09:55:50', '2022-03-30 09:56:35'),
