(1908, '2022/03/30', '5:41 p.m.', '1', '8', 'Adelaide Brown', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Juno Galang', NULL, NULL, 'Attended Ontime', 'Yes', 'Completed', 'N/A', 'N/A', NULL, '<p>Adelaide did a coaching session today regarding planning a narrative! We went through the writing process and narrative structure (beginning: hook, middle: conflict, and end: resolution/plot twist). Adelaide also created a sci-fi setting, characters, and a plot outline. Adelaide had very little difficulty in completing this -- the only difficulty was getting distracted from the task! However, we managed to complete the entire planning assignment. She did need reminding on the special bits to include for each section of a narrative, but readily composed plot points after she understood.</p>', NULL, '2022-03-30 17:42:00', '2022-03-30 17:42:29'),
