(2023, '2022/05/04', '08:46 am', '2', '1', 'Luke  Vandenberg', 'English', 'Writing - Sentence Construction & Vocabulary', 'Elements of a compound sentence > Capital letter, two independent clauses joined by a coordinating conjunction (FANBOYS), ending punctuation', 'Articulate/Explain the elements of a compound sentence (include use of manipulatives)', 'Yina Peng', 'Achieved', 'Achieved', 'Attended Ontime', 'N/A', 'Completed', 'N/A', 'N/A', NULL, '<p>Luke is a mature student who is quite commit to our learning.&nbsp;</p><p>We did writing assessment in sentence types and structures today.&nbsp;</p><ol><li>recapped sentence types and structures. Luke was introduced to these concepts and he knows the basic formation of each type and structure, yet he has not build a strong awareness of the key features of them. He needed help with complex sentence and compound sentence.&nbsp;</li><li>Assessment. We did this on the basis of discussion.</li></ol>', NULL, '2022-05-04 08:47:43', '2022-05-04 08:53:20'),
