(2067, '2022/05/09', '10:14 pm', '2', '1', 'Harlow Booy', 'Mathematics', 'Number & Place Value', 'Explore the connection between addition and subtraction', 'TEXT BOOK - EXERCISES, QUESTIONS, ACTIVITIES', 'Ivan Botero', 'Not Yet', 'N/A', 'Attended Ontime', 'Yes', 'Completed', 'Assigned', 'N/A', '<p>We did skip counting today one more time to help Harlow to see the connection between Additions and Subtractions.&nbsp;</p><p>Also, using the wheel, we went out to measure some spaces around. We played “council officers” took some measurements around the house and create a table to record the distances.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '<p>Harlow came today from 3:00 to 4:30 pm as she had to catch up on one lesson from term 1. All are up to date with her tutoring time as from today. &nbsp;</p>', '2022-05-09 22:14:27', '2022-07-02 11:23:03'),
