(2447, '2022/06/08', '03:28 pm', '2', '5', 'Max Brookfield', 'English', 'Systematic Phonics - Sounds/Symbols (phonograms)', 'Precisely say and write common phonograms (include purpose - to connect speech sounds to their written symbol which helps with reading, writing and spelling)', 'Oral Phonogram Review (OPR) - Various Phonograms (see notes)', 'Neve Mitchell', 'In Progress', 'N/A', 'Attended Ontime', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-06-08 15:28:17', '2022-06-08 16:23:45'),
(2448, '2022/06/08', '03:29 pm', '2', '6', 'Luke Gomer', 'English', 'Systematic Phonics - Language Rules (Pronunciation/Spelling/Grammar)', 'Rule 11: Drop the silent final \'e\' when adding a vowel ending/suffix', 'See Notes', 'Laree Thorsby', NULL, NULL, 'Attended Ontime', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', NULL, '<p>Focus this week was on completing the writing task.&nbsp;</p><p>Introduce a second speaker (commentator) and model appropriate use of speech in text.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2022-06-08 15:29:32', '2022-06-15 15:29:29');
