(2772, '2022/07/27', '03:29 pm', '3', '1', 'Max Brookfield', 'English', 'Phonological & Phonemic Awareness', 'Understand that spoken words consist of sequences of sounds called phonemes', 'Delete syllable from three syllable word - Kilpatrick Level E', 'Neve Mitchell', 'Achieved', 'N/A', 'Attended Ontime', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', NULL, '<figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>OPR: 27-70 + 45-60 second go through</td></tr><tr><td>WPR: ea aw au or ck wh ed igh</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>Rule 2 review. Discussion on whiteboard (revisited a lot of spiel elements). Cut &amp; Paste activity.&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>Use words from activity in sentences given to MB by NM. Oral work with sentence prior to writing and ID any words we are uncertain of the spelling for. NM provide spelling on whiteboard.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>Oral Fluency: Fitzroy 1. 77words in 50s. Fitzroy 2: 44wpm</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>Had a \'train\' of activities on the boards with a chocolate reward. This worked well to keep Max on track, although he was almost TOO conscious of time, trying to hurry himself along and not engaging.&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>', NULL, '2022-07-27 15:29:25', '2022-08-03 15:37:28'),
