(2832, '2022/08/03', '03:28 pm', '3', '2', 'Luke Gomer', 'English', 'Writing - Paragraph & Composition Construction', 'The Writing Process - Plan, Compose, Revise, Edit, Publish (by reading, speaking, media presentation)', 'Use the writing process to compose informative paragraph', 'Laree Thorsby', NULL, NULL, 'Attended Ontime', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', NULL, '<p>T3 W2</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>OPR/WPR</p><p>Vowels + s c k ck j dge g &nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Rule review&nbsp;</p><p>Job 2</p><p>R4/5/6/23</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>SD: Sect Q from Dew due include allow position ledge claim primary result</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Writing:</p><p>Week 1 use this in week 2 to assist with the writing task below.In class – Mind map on board.</p><p>FIFA World Cup 2022</p><p>What is it?</p><p>When is it?</p><p>Where is it?</p><p>Which countries are involved?</p><p>How many teams?</p><p>Can any team join?</p><p>How does qualifying work?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Week 3Choose your favourite&nbsp;team -?????</p><p>How many matches does ??????? play to qualify?</p><p>Who are their opponents?</p><p>Where are their games played?</p><p>How many games do they need to win to play in the WC?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Week 2 Worksheet &nbsp;(incomplete HW)</p><p>Choose your favourite player?</p><p>Use the WWWWWWH questions to write a paragraph about your player.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Plan</strong> your writing.</p><p><strong>Compose</strong> a draft.</p><p><strong>Revise&nbsp;</strong>your draft. - HW</p><p><strong>Edit</strong> your draft. -W 3</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Reading OF 514&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>HW – complete worksheet</p><p>Reading.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2022-08-03 15:28:49', '2022-08-03 17:04:34'),
