(2838, '2022/08/03', '04:36 pm', '3', '2', 'Xavier Schmidt', 'English', 'Writing - Paragraph & Composition Construction', 'The Writing Process - Plan, Compose, Revise, Edit, Publish (by reading, speaking, media presentation)', 'Use the writing process to compose informative paragraph', 'Laree Thorsby', NULL, NULL, 'Attended Ontime', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', NULL, '<p>Today Xave brought along his HASS assessment task on the Vietnam War. He had designed his first question and we brainstormed on the board the causes and consequences of Americans\' decision to invade Vietnam. Xavier had many great suggestions and completed a &nbsp;full paragraph of his draft on his laptop.&nbsp;</p><p>Spelling - short focus session on reinfircing the use of &nbsp;dge j g &nbsp;ck c k.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2022-08-03 16:36:45', '2022-08-05 09:22:29'),
