(2904, '2022/08/10', '03:29 pm', '3', '3', 'Luke Gomer', 'English', 'Systematic Phonics & Morphology - The Vocabulary of Word Structure', 'Suffix - letters added to the end of base words or word roots to create new words > they have their own meaning & they change the meaning of the base or root - Suffixes cannot stand/be used alone', 'Spell words with suffixes indicating number > s/es/ren', 'Laree Thorsby', NULL, NULL, 'Attended Ontime', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', NULL, '<p>T3 W3</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>OPR/WPR</p><p>Vowels + oi oy or ti ci si wh th f v l s&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Rule review&nbsp;</p><p>29 4 14&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>SD: Sect Q from appoint information who whom arrest them self themselves calf calves half halves</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Spelling rule worksheet for plurals ending with f.&nbsp;</p><p>Calf knife wife life elf shelf&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Writing:</p><p>Continue with writing task</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Worksheet&nbsp;(incomplete HW)</p><p>Choose your favourite player?</p><p>Use the WWWWWWH questions to write a paragraph about your player.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Plan</strong> your writing.</p><p><strong>Compose</strong> a draft.</p><p><strong>Revise&nbsp;</strong>your draft. - HW</p><p><strong>Edit</strong> your draft. -W 3</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Reading OF 514</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>HW – complete revise and edit</p><p>Reading.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, '2022-08-10 15:29:42', '2022-08-15 21:19:34'),
