(2951, '2022/08/16', '04:36 pm', '3', '4', 'Shay Douglas', 'Academic Coaching', 'Independent Study', 'School Assigned Worksheet or Assignment', 'See Notes', 'Neve Mitchell', 'Achieved', 'N/A', 'Attended Ontime', 'N/A', 'Completed', 'N/A', 'N/A', NULL, '<figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>Subject: Geography</td></tr><tr><td>Focus: Shay\'s Geography assignment.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>Shay once again requested independent learning time to work on his Geography assignment from school. He needed to create a few short paragraphs outlining his solution for the current housing crisis in Tasmania, and address a reason that could be argued against Shay\'s point.&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>We did discuss Shay\'s general points, which created a verbal outline. Shay also found himself getting stuck on finding statistics for a certain point in his argument. We discussed potentially flagging that for later, and instead using this time to compose a first draft before he would go back and add research support.&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>', NULL, '2022-08-16 16:36:54', '2022-08-16 16:57:35'),
