(2990, '2022/08/19', '03:36 pm', '3', '4', 'Connor Thompson ', 'Mathematics', 'Linear & Non-Linear Relationships', 'Linear relationships (Co-ordinates, Cartesian Plane)', 'School-assigned worksheet/task', 'Neve Mitchell', 'In Progress', 'N/A', 'Attended Ontime', 'N/A', 'Completed', 'N/A', 'N/A', NULL, '<figure class=\"table\"><table><tbody><tr><td>Maths -- Connor\'s \"Online Maths\"</td></tr><tr><td>Worked through the problems assigned by Connor\'s teacher. Predominately linear equation based, and Connor was able to complete most of them independently after we had covered/revised the following: gradient, y-int, formula.</td></tr><tr><td>Connor wasn\'t too tricky to manage this lesson, he found the work a little boring and was entertaining himself by drawing on the magnet, putting too much on the board (e.g. writing and erasing grad/y-int every time even though I repeatedly pointed out that the point of using the white board was so he didn\'t have to.&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>', NULL, '2022-08-19 15:36:31', '2022-08-19 16:26:11'),
