d her to check her spelling on the word court, she had to read back through her sentence to identify which word it was.</td></tr><tr><td>I\'m worried about her ability to remember and apply the rules. Maybe some rule drill sheets for homework? Could send home 2x a week to prompt her memory.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>', NULL, '2022-08-30 15:30:22', '2022-08-30 16:47:12'),
