(3253, '2022/09/15', '03:34 pm', '3', '8', 'Cara Lashmar', 'English', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Laree Thorsby', NULL, NULL, 'Attended Ontime', 'No', 'N/A', 'N/A', 'N/A', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2022-09-15 15:34:18', '2022-09-15 15:34:18'),
(3254, '2022/09/15', '04:21 pm', '3', '8', 'Callisto Pratten', 'Mathematics', 'Linear & Non-Linear Relationships', 'Linear & Non-linear equations', 'School-assigned worksheet/task', 'Rosemary Beswick', 'In Progress', 'In Progress', 'Attended Ontime', 'N/A', 'Completed', 'N/A', 'N/A', '<p>Callisto had not completed her subject selection for 2023 and so we worked on that for the first part of the session. We then discussed a strategy for revising for her test which is tomorrow. We agreed to work on improving the parts of the unit that she has completed, rather than trying to finish the bits that she has not. She started work on the Bivariate Data section of the 2021 exam. I gave her the 2020 exam to take home too and emailed her the links to the answers for both papers. She seems confident that she can pass. I think she has a way to go…</p>', NULL, NULL, '2022-09-15 16:21:12', '2022-09-15 18:36:16'),
